rComments: This prof is very intelligent and speaks well. Also very caring about her students and their grade. Even if the lectures were heavy, she explains everything clearly. She's organized, punctual and gives lots of good feedback throughout the semester. Make sure to do ALL of the readings and participate during group discussions to get your points!

C'est une excellente professeure car elle explique bien les concepts parfois plus difficile à comprendre. Elle est aussi très disponible à rencontrer les étudiants au besoin.  La méthode d'évaluation est:  un examen de mi-session maison, un travail écrit et un examen final. Je reprendrais ce cours dès demain!
She's a very cool teacher ! She's young, teachs well, speaks well and very intelligent. She really cares about her students and like to help them. If you can take a class with her. Amazing teach ! A+
